Package com.example.eventplanner

Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.eventplanner.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.os.Parcelable
public class Event extends Object implements android.os.Parcelable
The Event class represents an event in the event planner application. It implements the Parcelable interface to allow for passing instances of this class between components.
